sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant UI as Staff List Page
    participant LW as Livewire Component
    participant DB as Database

    User->>UI: Open staff list page
    UI->>LW: Initial request
    LW->>DB: Query staff/admin users with role and permissions
    DB-->>LW: Paginated staff result
    LW-->>UI: Render table and filters

    User->>UI: Search/filter/role/permission/sort/paginate
    UI->>LW: Update bound properties
    LW->>DB: Re-query with conditions
    DB-->>LW: Updated page result
    LW-->>UI: Re-render table

    User->>UI: Delete staff account
    UI->>LW: deleteStaff(id)
    alt Attempt self-delete
        LW-->>UI: Error toast
    else Valid delete
        LW->>DB: Delete target staff user
        alt Success
            DB-->>LW: Deleted
            LW-->>UI: Success toast
        else In use
            DB-->>LW: QueryException
            LW-->>UI: Error toast
        end
    end
